data.description: Escape to the charming home previously used as a bed and breakfast (The Inn of the Patriots) nestled in the heart of Grover, NC. Also is home to the US Presidential Culinary Museum. This expansive property boasts a large primary residence with multiple living areas perfect for hosting guests or relaxing with loved ones. The 3 car detached garage provides ample space for vehicles and storage. A home theater, large craft room, library with home office, and gym are ready for you! Situated near Kings Mountain and Shelby and under a hour from Uptown Charlotte, this small town beauty offers endless opportunities for outdoor adventures. Discover serenity at 301 Cleveland Ave in Grover, NC.
